\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The template is a legal HTML page.
 But there are marker in the page to tell Lift how to interpret the HTML.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
If the 
\family typewriter
<body>
\family default
 tag contains a 
\family typewriter
class
\family default
